reviewText: I have been a fan of the Power Rangers for many years.  In addition to the toys, I also try to collect as many of the videos and DVDs as I can.  I searched for this tape when it first came out in the 1990s, but I couldn't find it anywhere.  So when I found it on Amazon, I knew that I had to buy it as soon as possible.  Thank you for sending this out to me.
